{"tid":142084,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 韌帶整傷一問","createTime":"2017-03-03T12:40:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T05:48:47.000Z","uid":30447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67c65102e94d03f9cf061d20aa3400c06b306efe","tid":142084,"uid":30447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"喺英國2月14整傷半月板韌帶（醫生話係ligament torn），英國醫院一拖再拖3月14先做磁力共振掃描，3月21再覆診。<br />\n佢話要做手術，但起碼都要四月先有得做。<br />\n擔心咁樣拖成兩個月會唔會無事都變有事？<br />\n<br />\n上面段嘢係我個frd借我account問<br />\n補充一下  佢整親之後一個星期都冇返學 <br />\n最近返學都有盡量唔用整親隻腳受力<br />\n同埋有用醫生俾嘅嘢固定隻腳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yf62FTJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYf62FTJ.jpg&h=fda05d07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有冇巴打有類似經驗或者知識講下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e625f2693f418300e43cda738361ed54e82ca7","tid":142084,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:44:43.000Z","msg":"而家做同遲啲做，基本上無乜分别。<br />\n如果你急想做，就另外自己揾醫生睇下有無檔期。"},{"pid":"38f4f8b769d6c090246099c7a3b4ec4133792ddb","tid":142084,"uid":30447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T12:50:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家做同遲啲做，基本上無乜分别。<br />\n如果你急想做，就另外自己揾醫生睇下有無檔期。</blockquote><br />\n即係維持而家咁樣  直到正式接受治療都無問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ec18be1159ba6117341a25012d4beab35ff8b18","tid":142084,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:22:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]而家做同遲啲做，基本上無乜分别。<br />\n如果你急想做，就另外自己揾醫生睇下有無檔期。</blockquote><br />\n即係維持而家咁樣  直到正式接受治療都無問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote<br />\n<br />\n係呀，無問题。<br />\n呢類手術，遲一兩個月先做手術，基本上無乜問題，因為都斷左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至多係怕佢縮短左而駁唔到。<br />\n但呢個情况要再長啲時間先至會<br />\n<br />\nbtw,其實你擔心乜野呢？<br />\n<br />\n以上如果有錯，請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8301b6f596111f04438e6711131b278528d86e4f","tid":142084,"uid":54534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"半月板+靭帶傷定斷<br />\n但其實無咩分別。<br />\n我依家係ACL tear 半月板無事<br />\n都無呢舊野帶 係出街拎兩枝叉<br />\n消腫 練大脾。等做手術移植<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒敷冰 消下腫"},{"pid":"187c8eea7e79a7f74d523578e76cf79ac74ee21a","tid":142084,"uid":30447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:31:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>[quote]而家做同遲啲做，基本上無乜分别。<br />\n如果你急想做，就另外自己揾醫生睇下有無檔期。</blockquote><br />\n即係維持而家咁樣  直到正式接受治療都無問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote<br />\n<br />\n係呀，無問题。<br />\n呢類手術，遲一兩個月先做手術，基本上無乜問題，因為都斷左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n至多係怕佢縮短左而駁唔到。<br />\n但呢個情况要再長啲時間先至會<br />\n<br />\nbtw,其實你擔心乜野呢？<br />\n<br />\n以上如果有錯，請指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n主要都係驚拖得耐有可能會惡化啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n順手想屌下英國啲醫生同醫院揸流攤同慢嘅程度好撚厲害"},{"pid":"1d9300afba781770a876e27bf065a965da87b79d","tid":142084,"uid":30447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>半月板+靭帶傷定斷<br />\n但其實無咩分別。<br />\n我依家係ACL tear 半月板無事<br />\n都無呢舊野帶 係出街拎兩枝叉<br />\n消腫 練大脾。等做手術移植<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒敷冰 消下腫</blockquote><br />\n練大脾可以點練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4898de1fd595ad570bb4fa1fff9bbbe34d8be18e","tid":142084,"uid":85899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T13:42:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>半月板+靭帶傷定斷<br />\n但其實無咩分別。<br />\n我依家係ACL tear 半月板無事<br />\n都無呢舊野帶 係出街拎兩枝叉<br />\n消腫 練大脾。等做手術移植<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒敷冰 消下腫</blockquote><br />\n練大脾可以點練<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n坐喺度用兩個膝頭夾住本書唔好比佢跌落地，維持幾分鐘或者加重量"},{"pid":"b993455b362290a7d9ec2d8aaad0f4faffeba287","tid":142084,"uid":30447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:55:32.000Z","msg":"有冇人知大概幾耐之後可以做得返劇烈運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"850a3c1b6af0e9d4266f726d7fbf475415c6f99b","tid":142084,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知大概幾耐之後可以做得返劇烈運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做完之後幾個月啦"},{"pid":"d0670dfb4ccca65cd3b7e4ea3b87553881eb496a","tid":142084,"uid":54534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:30:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知大概幾耐之後可以做得返劇烈運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n照道理 快既都半年 <br />\n做完手術頭一兩個月都係要比佢抖下"},{"pid":"f5dc0bbf032e2d158df58878d7eea0dd809a3d12","tid":142084,"uid":69487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人知大概幾耐之後可以做得返劇烈運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n做完手術後快嘅話半年可以慢慢投入番<br />\n如果身體碰撞性好高嘅運動，一般都要大概9個月左右"}]}